714095f-a.text:
61st Street, west from Lexington Ave., showing mainly the north side. The large apartment houses seen are at the N.E. and N.W. corners of Park Ave. Note the street car tracks on Lexington Ave. which will shortly be removed; gasoline busses replacing the former
method of transportation in 1936.
April 9, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
